{{Infobox dungeon |name = Sky Pillar |image = [[File:Sky Pillar.png|300px]] |caption = An outside view of Sky Pillar. |tokens = 34,000 |location = Southwest of Sootopolis City, north of Route 131. }} '''Sky Pillar''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Hoenn]]. It initially has 49 tiles arranged in a 7x7 square, including 7 chest tiles, 17 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
